OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1777190772
OL,3,C'Most likely' Noah Donohoe entered
OL,4,Ctunnel through bars of culvert entrance
OL,6,FIt is "most likely" that Noah Donohoe
OL,7,Fentered a water tunnel through the
OL,8,Fbars of a culvert entrance close to
OL,9,Fwhere he was last seen, an inquest
OL,10,Finto his death has heard.
OL,12,FBelfast Coroner's Court heard evidence
OL,13,Ffrom engineering experts about the
OL,14,Fculvert on Friday afternoon as the
OL,15,Finquest into the death of the
OL,16,Fschoolboy finished its 12th week.
OL,18,FNoah, a pupil at St Malachy's College,
OL,19,Fwas 14 when his naked body was found
OL,20,Fin a water tunnel in north Belfast on
OL,21,FJune 27 2020.
OL,26,@nD@GOUnD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1777190772
OL,3,C'Most likely' Noah Donohoe entered
OL,4,Ctunnel through bars of culvert entrance
OL,6,FIt was six days after leaving home on
OL,7,Fhis bike to meet two friends in the
OL,8,FCavehill area of the city.
OL,10,FA post-mortem examination found the
OL,11,Flikely cause of death was drowning.
OL,13,FThe court heard evidence from civil
OL,14,Fengineer Brian Pope and expert in risk
OL,15,Fassessment Dr Mark Cooper on Friday.
OL,17,FThey were among a group of four
OL,18,Fexperts who had had their joint
OL,19,Fresponses to a series of questions
OL,20,Fread to the inquest earlier in the
OL,21,Fmonth.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1777190772
OL,3,C'Most likely' Noah Donohoe entered
OL,4,Ctunnel through bars of culvert entrance
OL,6,FThey were questioned by counsel for
OL,7,Fthe coroner Peter Coll KC about the
OL,8,Fculvert entrance close to homes on
OL,9,FPremier Drive and Northwood Road in
OL,10,Fnorth Belfast.
OL,12,FThe culvert leads to a tunnel network
OL,13,Fin which Noah's body was found.
OL,15,FMr Coll said the experts had concluded
OL,16,Fin their joint response Noah was most
OL,17,Flikely to have entered the culvert
OL,18,Fthrough the grille in Northwood Linear
OL,19,FPark.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1777190772
OL,3,C'Most likely' Noah Donohoe entered
OL,4,Ctunnel through bars of culvert entrance
OL,6,FMr Pope told the jury: "I felt that it
OL,7,Fwas most likely that access was gained
OL,8,Fbetween the bars.
OL,10,F"There was approximately 180
OL,11,Fmillimetres gap, which is adequate for
OL,12,Fa larger child or a young person to
OL,13,Fsqueeze through.
OL,15,F"So, geometrically, I felt that that
OL,16,Fwas the most likely.
OL,18,F"Manholes are very difficult to lift
OL,19,Fand need special keys.
OL,26,@nD@XOUrD@AOUwD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1777190772
OL,3,C'Most likely' Noah Donohoe entered
OL,4,Ctunnel through bars of culvert entrance
OL,6,F"So, I felt that the at the inlet was
OL,7,Fthe most likely point, there is a
OL,8,Fhatch above that wasn't locked."
OL,10,FMr Pope said he did not believe the
OL,11,Ftunnel outlet at Belfast Lough was a
OL,12,Fpossible entry point.
OL,14,FHe said: "It's in a tidal situation
OL,15,Fand not easily seen. It would not be
OL,16,Fan attractive way to enter the
OL,17,Fculvert."
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@`O]vD@JOUyD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1777190772
OL,3,C'Most likely' Noah Donohoe entered
OL,4,Ctunnel through bars of culvert entrance
OL,6,FDr Cooper said he had been shown a
OL,7,Fphotograph of an adult squeezing
OL,8,Fthrough the bars at the culvert
OL,9,Fentrance.
OL,11,FHe said: "I just thought that that was
OL,12,Fvery persuasive."
OL,14,FMr Pope told the jury that the normal
OL,15,Fway for someone to have moved along
OL,16,Fthe tunnel would have been "crouching
OL,17,For crawling".
OL,26,@sD@JOUtD@QO]xD@\OUyD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1777190772
OL,3,C'Most likely' Noah Donohoe entered
OL,4,Ctunnel through bars of culvert entrance
OL,6,FAsked about access to the area where
OL,7,Fthe culvert was, Mr Pope said he
OL,8,Fbelieved it was prevented for the
OL,9,Fmajority of people due to
OL,10,F"substantial" fencing.
OL,12,FHowever, Dr Cooper said it was a
OL,13,F"mixed picture" over public access,
OL,14,Fpointing out there was no fencing at
OL,15,Fthe rear of houses close to the park.
OL,17,FMr Coll said the joint response
OL,18,Fprovided to the inquest by the experts
OL,19,Fsaid the culvert would have created
OL,20,Fthe conditions for drowning.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@MO]uD@AOUuD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1777190772
OL,3,C'Most likely' Noah Donohoe entered
OL,4,Ctunnel through bars of culvert entrance
OL,6,FMr Pope said: "I think with the
OL,7,Fclimatic conditions, the cold, the
OL,8,Fdarkness, potential confusion.
OL,10,F"I'm an engineer, I understand
OL,11,Fpipework, but if you were not au fait
OL,12,Fwith that, it would be a very
OL,13,Fconfusing situation."
OL,15,FMr Coll said there would be a
OL,16,Fdifference between an experienced
OL,17,FDepartment for Infrastructure (DFI)
OL,18,Foperative in protective clothing
OL,19,Fentering the tunnel compared to a
OL,20,Fmember of the public.
OL,26,@nD@OOUrD@AOUuD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1777190772
OL,3,C'Most likely' Noah Donohoe entered
OL,4,Ctunnel through bars of culvert entrance
OL,6,FMr Pope said: "It would be a
OL,7,Fcompletely different scenario,
OL,8,Fcompared to being in the dark tunnel
OL,9,Fand by yourself."
OL,11,FBarrister for the DFI Neasa Murnaghan
OL,12,FKC asked the two experts to confirm
OL,13,Fthere was a difference between a
OL,14,Fsecurity screen over a culvert and a
OL,15,Fdebris screen, which has more space
OL,16,Fbetween the bars.
OL,18,FBoth witnesses agreed.
OL,26,@nD@OOUqD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/11
